commit.message:
configure.ac: Use AC_USE_SYSTEM_EXTENSIONS

And to make it effective, include <config.c> at the start of C files
(except those compiled from Vala).  This is necessary to obtain a
declaration of ptsname in <stdlib.h>.

BUG=https://github.com/fujiwarat/ibus-fbterm/pull/1

configure.ac: Make compatible with autoconf 2.71

Newer autoconf versions require declarations for certain macro
patterns.

commit.message: Update ibus-fbterm.1 to descript Enter key on IME switcher
Make sure ibus-daemon is not running before ibus-fbterm is called
Add a man page of ibus-fbterm
Set scrolling region not to draw the existent prompts

Use GIOChannel insteadd of epoll

Delete FbIoDispatcher so that callbacks of IBusInputContext work.

Integrate ibus-fbterm

This does not use fbterm protocol of $FBTERM_IM_SOCKET so that
keybindings can be handled by ibus but not fbterm.
